Dependencies that need to be installed
libusb-1.0

To run the regression tests, you will need http://www.eyrie.org/~eagle/software/c-tap-harness/


To Build

    make

Installing library on Fedora x86_64 target:

    install -m 755 libcyusbserial.so.1 /usr/lib64
    ln -sf libcyusbserial.so.1 /usr/lib64/libcyusbserial.so

Installing library on Ubuntu x86_64 target:

    install -m 755 libcyusbserial.so.1 /usr/lib
    ln -sf libcyusbserial.so.1 /usr/lib/libcyusbserial.so

Installing binaries:

    install -m 755 cyMUX cytool /usr/bin

cyMUX should be run as a service during start up.
